gthen, comfort, and by Thy power quickly grant them relief, freedom, and deliverance. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1\afs20 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f47\fs20\cf6\insrsid8156083\charrsid14484228 Bow.
